4.1	Outcomes of the Internship
The 4 Months internship at Besant Technology yielded significant outcomes. A fully functional web application was developed and tested, demonstrating the practical application of Full Stack Development and QA Testing principles.
•	Developed a complete web application with React.js frontend and Node.js/Express.js backend.
•	Implemented JWT-based authentication and role-based access control.
•	Written and executed over 100 manual test cases covering functional and regression scenarios.
•	Automated key test scenarios using Selenium and Jest, reducing manual testing effort by ~40%.
•	Performed API testing with Postman and tracked 30+ bugs through JIRA.



